sri-project-8 | Low-Cost Production of Titanium Alloys | http://www.sri.com/work/projects/low-cost-production-titanium-alloys | description:SRI is developing an advanced process that reacts titanium tetrachloride and other metal chlorides with hydrogen to produce titanium or titanium alloy granules in a single step.
sri-project-9 | Membrane System for Pre-Combustion-Based Carbon Capture | http://www.sri.com/work/projects/membrane-based-system-pre-combustion-based-carbon-dioxide-capture | description:SRI’s porous membrane technology offers greater efficiency and lower emissions for coal-based electrical generation.
sri-project-10 | Mixed Salt Process for Carbon Dioxide Separation | http://www.sri.com/work/projects/mixed-salt-process-carbon-dioxide-separation | description:SRI’s mixed salt process uses known solvents in a new way to dramatically improve the economics of carbon capture.
sri-project-11 | Remediating Unexploded Ordnance | http://www.sri.com/work/projects/remediating-unexploded-ordnance | description:SRI has developed a novel approach to safely and efficiently render harmless weapons and ammunition that are no longer needed for military use.
sri-project-12 | Silicon/Air Battery for “Vanishing” Electronic Systems | http://www.sri.com/work/projects/silicon-air-battery-vanishing-electronics | description:To meet an important military challenge, SRI is designing a sensor system that can disappear on command.
